name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
info: ***1ST & 2ND DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!! name: Thurston County Public Health Medical Reserve Corp
address: Thurston County Fairgrounds - 2790 Carpenter Rd SE , Lacey WA, 98503
info:
This is a Moderna vaccination event for anyone age 18 and older. 

• This is a drive-thru clinic at Thurston County Fairgrounds. Please use the Long Lake Park entrance, 2790 Carpenter Rd SE, Lacey 98503. The clinic time is 8:00am - 1:00pm. • Please bring a form of identification with you to your appointment - ID card, passport, or other document with your name and birthday on it.• Wear a short-sleeved shirt, but dress with layers, if necessary. • Waiting at least 15 minutes after vaccination is required.
